data.description: PRICE REDUCED! MOTIVATED SELLER! Home back on market through no fault of seller. 3000+ SF, 5-bedroom, 3-bath home in desirable Fox Farm area.  Remodeled kitchen, stainless steel appliances.  Two dining areas or one off the kitchen can be used as a family room.  Large living room with wood-burning fireplace.  Master bedroom has ensuite bathroom.  Large newly carpeted family room downstairs with gas fireplace, plus two more bedrooms.  Large laundry room with washer/dryer, storage, laundry tub.  Upright freezer included.  Large utilities room with great storage. Fenced backyard with large composite deck, hot tub, two garden sheds, and a fire pit.  Two-car garage with shelving.  Near Meadowlark School and close to shopping. Nest doorbell and thermostat.
